column5: I just checked out www.LeBaron.ca and its main page say something about MidNight Madness May 3 @ Midngiht to 7AM.
Was in there today,  they have a sale on 3rd-5th, lots of good deals coming up, each day different stuff on sale, you have to check their site to find out what.
Where do you see that info. I cant find it on their site.
probably to compete with the s.a..i.l opening here in montreal on the 3rd.4.5.6

Just clicked on the link and it works no priblem, but look on the top middle ...... I can't believe Diawa called their reel "SOL". I don't know what that means to you, but it doesn't seem like a good endorsement to me LOL  . "Hey Joe", whad'ya catch today?" Reply ..... nothing , "SOL" today".
